\markdownSetup{unicodeNormalizationForm=nfd}
<<<
This test ensures that the Lua `unicodeNormalization` option is enabled by default
and that the Lua `unicodeNormalizationForm` option correctly propagates through
the plain TeX interface.

The Unicode character *ϔ* (U+03D2 U+0308) should be left unnormalized.
>>>
BEGIN document
codeSpan: unicodeNormalization
softLineBreak
codeSpan: unicodeNormalizationForm
softLineBreak
paragraphSeparator
emphasis: ϔ
END document
